Class QuantizedResultSet<O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.ResultSet<O>
      • com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.filter.FilteringResultSet<O>
        • com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.filter.QuantizedResultSet<O>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<O>

    public class QuantizedResultSet<O>
extends FilteringResultSet<O>
    An implementation of FilteringResultSet which filters objects based on whether they match a given query.

    This can be useful to index which use a Quantizer.

    Author:
    Niall Gallagher
